## Description of Service

Flexecution is a workout tracking, planning, and daily health logging application with voice commands and social fitness features. The App allows you to:

- Log workouts with detailed exercise and set tracking
- Use voice commands to log sets, add exercises, and adjust weights hands-free
- Complete daily health check-ins via voice or manual input
- Track personal records and achievements
- Create and manage reusable workout templates with custom exercise icons
- Generate workout programs using linear and double progression calculators
- Schedule workouts on a calendar with notification reminders
- Export workouts to your device's calendar or as shareable ICS files
- Generate and share workout summary cards
- Log daily health metrics including body measurements, wellness data, and notes
- View interactive progress charts and analytics
- Compete against your past performance in Ghost Battles
- Fight progressively harder bosses in Boss Battles
- Invite friends and battle together using Co-op Buddies via iCloud
- Use a rest timer between sets

All core data is stored locally on your device. Co-op Buddies data is synced through Apple's iCloud (CloudKit) and shared only with friends you explicitly invite.

