## Health and Fitness Disclaimer

Flexecution is a fitness tracking and scheduling tool, not a medical device. The App does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.

- Workout programs generated by the App (including linear progression and double progression plans) are auto-generated scheduling aids and are not reviewed or recommended by a medical or fitness professional. They are intended to help you stay consistent and organize your training.
- Daily health check-in data (body weight, sleep, mood, energy, stress, water intake, calories, protein) is for personal tracking only and does not constitute health monitoring or medical assessment.
- Voice commands are a convenience feature and should not be relied upon for accuracy — always verify logged data.
- Gamification features (Ghost Battles, Boss Battles) are motivational tools and should not encourage overtraining or unsafe exercise practices.

Always consult a qualified healthcare professional before beginning any new exercise program. You use the App and follow any workout plans at your own risk.

